Title: Series: Library of Ashurbanipal
Description: Part of a clay prism, annals of Ashurbanipal, revolt of Tashdamane of Egypt, 2nd campaign against Egypt, end of 4th campaign against Kirbit (?), commencement of 5th campaign, against Ahsheri, 11 + 7 lines of inscription, Neo-Assyrian.
Bibliographic references: Lambert & Millard 1968a / Catalogue of the cuneiform tablets in the Kouyunjik Collection of the British Museum: Second Supplement
